@abstract:
Trust and provenance verification for Wokelangiser.
Maximal trust by default — LLM may read, build, test, lint, format.
@end

@trust-level: maximal
@trust-boundary: repo
@trust-actions: [read, build, test, lint, format]
@trust-deny: [delete-branch, force-push, modify-ci-secrets, publish]

## Integrity

### license-content
- description: LICENSE declares MPL-2.0 and both REUSE licence texts are present
- run: grep -q 'MPL-2.0' LICENSE && test -f LICENSES/MPL-2.0.txt && test -f LICENSES/CC-BY-SA-4.0.txt
- severity: critical

### no-secrets-committed
- description: No .env or credential files in repo
- run: test ! -f .env && test ! -f credentials.json && test ! -f .env.local
- severity: critical
